author: ajith
msg: 1. Updated the templates and the emitter to handle unwrapping in server side. Now the generated code for the message receivers can handle multiple inputs.
I. Added several new methods to the ADBDatabindingTemplate.xsl
2.Added a new property to the codegen-config.properties to store the names of the databinding frameworks that support unwrapping.
Now unwrapping is supported for server side as well but only for inputs. Needs a test case to verify the functionality.
